{"tid":1956092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 今晚8時齊為醫護鼓掌 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-04-03T03:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T12:43:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be4f89cbd553bce4f012ba6a1f9346f822b6def6","tid":1956092,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T03:08:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/NYBVHTRGHWSRIJRNYKBHGOKFB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FNYBVHTRGHWSRIJRNYKBHGOKFB4%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=43f90e0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FNYBVHTRGHWSRIJRNYKBHGOKFB4%2F&h=1f853572\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/NYBVHTRGHWSRIJRNYKBHGOKFB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n今晚8時齊為醫護鼓掌 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200403/large/1585846866_d1b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200403%2Flarge%2F1585846866_d1b8.jpg&h=ab564fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界各地近期陸續響應「為醫護鼓掌」（Clap For Carers）活動，其中英國威廉王子三名寶貝仔女，包括佐治王子、夏洛特公主、路易王子係肯辛頓宮，帶住燦爛嘅笑容，齊齊拍掌一幕最令人窩心。<br />\n<br />\n本港嘅太古地產愛心大使，今晚就會聯同其他機構參與「Clap For Carers為醫護鼓掌」活動，呼籲港人發揮正能量，晚上8時無論身在何方，都為本港嘅抗疫英雄，熱烈鼓掌最少一分鐘，希望集齊全港巿民掌聲，向正在守護病人、無私嘅醫護人員，表達衷心謝意、無言感激。太古地產愛心大使更專誠設計咗特別海報，集合眾人力量，呼籲更多市民參與。<br />\n<br />\n今次Clap For Carers源自英國一名來自荷蘭嘅女瑜伽導師，上月底喺Twitter發起呢個醫護鼓掌活動，呢個訊息之後獲大批網民轉發，包括皇室人員響應參與，令各地陸續加入。"},{"pid":"f5bfc98677174bdb272ba975b180be71684ab032","tid":1956092,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"多謝醫護<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07cb1536decc1a08e5e69ad6810d9a22bde55b5","tid":1956092,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200205/HDLF2UB2S4SBF5CLDTO4DHRBPE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200205%2FHDLF2UB2S4SBF5CLDTO4DHRBPE%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=87c3e229\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200205%2FHDLF2UB2S4SBF5CLDTO4DHRBPE%2F&h=84e3f664\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200205/HDLF2UB2S4SBF5CLDTO4DHRBPE/</a><br />\n<br />\n7,000醫護罷工 今登門促林鄭對話<br />\nDirty Team：犧牲都要有意義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【肺炎大爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】逾7,000名醫護昨參與醫管局員工陣線發動的第二階段罷工，再促政府封關救港。有被分配為Dirty Team的護士揚言，即使犧牲亦要「有意義咁死」。特首林鄭月娥及醫管局大打民意戰，均稱醫院的新生嬰兒深切治療部是缺勤重災區，促罷工醫護返回崗位，「BB真係好靠你哋照顧佢」。工會形容疫情已到臨界點，今早將與林鄭直接對話，視乎對方的回應再決定下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n記者：周詠雯 梁銘恩 鄧溢禧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580833749_d9af.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200205%2Flarge%2F1580833749_d9af.gif&h=9ea8f0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾3,500名罷工的醫護昨到醫管局大樓流水式遞交請願信。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580833747_6bc1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200205%2Flarge%2F1580833747_6bc1.gif&h=747d3768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有長者手持標語，支持醫護人員罷工。馬泉崇攝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580833748_4e3e.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200205%2Flarge%2F1580833748_4e3e.gif&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=2907f423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580833748_4e3e.gif</a><br />\n醫管局員工陣線表示，昨日逾7,000醫護參與第二階段罷工。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫護罷工聲勢浩大，醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明表示，超過7,000醫護參與第二階段罷工，佔醫管局總人手近一成。罷工醫護在各聯網的「龍頭醫院」門外排隊簽到，部份醫護掛上白絲帶。早上兩小時的罷工請願行動中，工會收集逾4,000張簽名請願信，成功轉交醫管局。<br />\n<br />\n下午各區醫院如伊利沙伯、瑪嘉烈、威爾斯親王醫院，門外亦有人龍，有醫護手持「醫護罷工促全面封關」、「全面封關救港」等標語，瑪嘉烈一度有約400人排隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怕病毒傳染 減少見家人<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：賀一誠封賭場半月 「買晒葡國口罩」<br />\n<br />\n有七年年資、被編入照顧懷疑或確診患者的隊伍（Dirty Team）的屯門醫院護士的盧先生表示，自己已經做好疫情爆發的心理準備，「我唔怕死，但我要有意義咁死，唔係好似隻棋咁死」。<br />\n<br />\n盧已在隔離病房工作兩周，擔心有可能病菌傳予家人，近期減少與母親見面。他指如果政府做好封關措施、為醫護提供充足準備，他完全不介意站在抗疫第一線。「但如果我係為咗政府無能而死，我覺得唔值」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣被編入Dirty Team的兒科醫生陳先生雖然如常當值，但仍到街站簽署罷工聲明。他說十分認同工會罷工的訴求，當醫管局不願意代員工發聲，醫護只能藉罷工表態。但他因身兼Dirty Team工作，需負責照顧和監察懷疑確診病人，為了避免其他同事代替他承受感染風險，最終決定「罷一半工」，不會執行任何非臨床和非緊急的工作，「我揸住個call機，如果有call我先至會做嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n醫護上下一心救港，但仍未撼動政權。醫管局聯網服務總監楊諦岡形容罷工對醫院運作有非常嚴重影響，部份非緊急服務手術都已取消，緊急重要服務亦受一定影響。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理（聯網運作）張子峯稱，罷工重災區為急症室醫護、另新生嬰兒深切治療部有一半醫護缺勤，他盼醫護回心轉意：「BB真係好靠你哋照顧佢，食奶、各樣嘢都係要靠你哋。」林鄭昨晨會見傳媒時亦說，不少病情危重的病人因罷工受影響，新生嬰兒深切治療部的情況「令人更傷心」，希望醫護回心轉意，為香港市民服務，但她繼續拒續回應訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580838765_a98a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200205%2Flarge%2F1580838765_a98a.jpg&h=7316750e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫管局：盼大家回心轉意<br />\n<br />\n楊諦岡又大打溫情牌，稱「我哋每位同事都非常緊要，今時今日一個都不能少」。他說同事的心聲和理據，全港人都聽到和明白。楊、張兩人先後最少五度強調要求罷工人員返回崗位，又指「病人始終喺醫院，希望大家回心轉意」，又向無參與罷工醫護致謝，提醒前線同事小心身體。<br />\n<br />\n余慧明形容，社會已進入臨界點，全港市民生命危在旦夕，封關刻不容緩。工會今早10時會到特首辦，呼籲林鄭直接與他們對話，如果對方仍拒絕，會再交代下一步行動。醫管局表示，截至昨晚六時，共有接近5,000名員工缺勤，包括大約360名醫生、2,800名護士及1,000名專職醫療人員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">多謝醫護</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a3c1381dd79cb7f706f49c46affc1e5247f64e","tid":1956092,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200205/HDLF2UB2S4SBF5CLDTO4DHRBPE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200205%2FHDLF2UB2S4SBF5CLDTO4DHRBPE%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=87c3e229\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200205%2FHDLF2UB2S4SBF5CLDTO4DHRBPE%2F&h=84e3f664\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200205/HDLF2UB2S4SBF5CLDTO4DHRBPE/</a><br />\n<br />\n7,000醫護罷工 今登門促林鄭對話<br />\nDirty Team：犧牲都要有意義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【肺炎大爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】逾7,000名醫護昨參與醫管局員工陣線發動的第二階段罷工，再促政府封關救港。有被分配為Dirty Team的護士揚言，即使犧牲亦要「有意義咁死」。特首林鄭月娥及醫管局大打民意戰，均稱醫院的新生嬰兒深切治療部是缺勤重災區，促罷工醫護返回崗位，「BB真係好靠你哋照顧佢」。工會形容疫情已到臨界點，今早將與林鄭直接對話，視乎對方的回應再決定下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n記者：周詠雯 梁銘恩 鄧溢禧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580833749_d9af.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200205%2Flarge%2F1580833749_d9af.gif&h=9ea8f0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾3,500名罷工的醫護昨到醫管局大樓流水式遞交請願信。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580833747_6bc1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200205%2Flarge%2F1580833747_6bc1.gif&h=747d3768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有長者手持標語，支持醫護人員罷工。馬泉崇攝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580833748_4e3e.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200205%2Flarge%2F1580833748_4e3e.gif&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=2907f423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580833748_4e3e.gif</a><br />\n醫管局員工陣線表示，昨日逾7,000醫護參與第二階段罷工。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫護罷工聲勢浩大，醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明表示，超過7,000醫護參與第二階段罷工，佔醫管局總人手近一成。罷工醫護在各聯網的「龍頭醫院」門外排隊簽到，部份醫護掛上白絲帶。早上兩小時的罷工請願行動中，工會收集逾4,000張簽名請願信，成功轉交醫管局。<br />\n<br />\n下午各區醫院如伊利沙伯、瑪嘉烈、威爾斯親王醫院，門外亦有人龍，有醫護手持「醫護罷工促全面封關」、「全面封關救港」等標語，瑪嘉烈一度有約400人排隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怕病毒傳染 減少見家人<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：賀一誠封賭場半月 「買晒葡國口罩」<br />\n<br />\n有七年年資、被編入照顧懷疑或確診患者的隊伍（Dirty Team）的屯門醫院護士的盧先生表示，自己已經做好疫情爆發的心理準備，「我唔怕死，但我要有意義咁死，唔係好似隻棋咁死」。<br />\n<br />\n盧已在隔離病房工作兩周，擔心有可能病菌傳予家人，近期減少與母親見面。他指如果政府做好封關措施、為醫護提供充足準備，他完全不介意站在抗疫第一線。「但如果我係為咗政府無能而死，我覺得唔值」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣被編入Dirty Team的兒科醫生陳先生雖然如常當值，但仍到街站簽署罷工聲明。他說十分認同工會罷工的訴求，當醫管局不願意代員工發聲，醫護只能藉罷工表態。但他因身兼Dirty Team工作，需負責照顧和監察懷疑確診病人，為了避免其他同事代替他承受感染風險，最終決定「罷一半工」，不會執行任何非臨床和非緊急的工作，「我揸住個call機，如果有call我先至會做嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n醫護上下一心救港，但仍未撼動政權。醫管局聯網服務總監楊諦岡形容罷工對醫院運作有非常嚴重影響，部份非緊急服務手術都已取消，緊急重要服務亦受一定影響。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理（聯網運作）張子峯稱，罷工重災區為急症室醫護、另新生嬰兒深切治療部有一半醫護缺勤，他盼醫護回心轉意：「BB真係好靠你哋照顧佢，食奶、各樣嘢都係要靠你哋。」林鄭昨晨會見傳媒時亦說，不少病情危重的病人因罷工受影響，新生嬰兒深切治療部的情況「令人更傷心」，希望醫護回心轉意，為香港市民服務，但她繼續拒續回應訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580838765_a98a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200205%2Flarge%2F1580838765_a98a.jpg&h=7316750e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫管局：盼大家回心轉意<br />\n<br />\n楊諦岡又大打溫情牌，稱「我哋每位同事都非常緊要，今時今日一個都不能少」。他說同事的心聲和理據，全港人都聽到和明白。楊、張兩人先後最少五度強調要求罷工人員返回崗位，又指「病人始終喺醫院，希望大家回心轉意」，又向無參與罷工醫護致謝，提醒前線同事小心身體。<br />\n<br />\n余慧明形容，社會已進入臨界點，全港市民生命危在旦夕，封關刻不容緩。工會今早10時會到特首辦，呼籲林鄭直接與他們對話，如果對方仍拒絕，會再交代下一步行動。醫管局表示，截至昨晚六時，共有接近5,000名員工缺勤，包括大約360名醫生、2,800名護士及1,000名專職醫療人員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">多謝醫護</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a51f51fa9db286c077142ed21ab6e6c7d33af68","tid":1956092,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:02:27.000Z","msg":"【抗疫兼抗暴政】行動post: 不如恢復十點和你嗌？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1956598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1956598</a>"},{"pid":"76e79d6f8404defb08a09e5ca714b39d15f8691c","tid":1956092,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"3 mins to go"},{"pid":"7d1f158987922422bc019f59df99a8d5bd94ccf1","tid":1956092,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"多謝醫護<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e99328f2ca7dce53fcf48ebca5d3d68fbcef633","tid":1956092,"uid":152711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"拍緊"},{"pid":"722855740ccd749466f32e9efb1ec025f77f1086","tid":1956092,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:04:02.000Z","msg":"係深水埗黃金附近拍咗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92a53a76923d12f2015a94f4de62add8364a08f","tid":1956092,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82412fb108826e30d00fae077d834ae8731d2cba","tid":1956092,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"多謝醫護<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1f500b6f2242b58056219fdb94ccac9571bb6b","tid":1956092,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:05:34.000Z","msg":"拍掌聲太細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4841a9b7ad267d24129be12a67381bd18140c20","tid":1956092,"uid":177194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"好on9<br />\n要拍去醫院拍啦"},{"pid":"46e5736c0938ca0a02666c2210808a30b93e5f48","tid":1956092,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"多謝醫護<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}